Sure! Here are some of the best colleges in the USA that provide professional training in guitar:

1. Berklee College of Music - Located in Boston, Massachusetts, Berklee College of Music is renowned for its guitar program. They offer a Bachelor of Music in Guitar Performance and have a faculty of world-class guitarists. [Visit Berklee College of Music](https://www.berklee.edu/){:target="_blank"}

2. The Juilliard School - Situated in New York City, The Juilliard School is known for its prestigious music programs. They offer a Bachelor of Music in Guitar Performance and have a rigorous curriculum designed to develop technical skills and musicality. [Visit The Juilliard School](https://www.juilliard.edu/){:target="_blank"}

3. University of Southern California (USC) Thornton School of Music - Located in Los Angeles, California, USC Thornton School of Music offers a Bachelor of Music in Studio/Jazz Guitar. They have a renowned faculty and provide opportunities for students to perform in various ensembles. [Visit USC Thornton School of Music](https://music.usc.edu/){:target="_blank"}

4. Manhattan School of Music - Situated in New York City, Manhattan School of Music offers a Bachelor of Music in Classical Guitar Performance. They have a comprehensive curriculum that focuses on technique, interpretation, and performance skills. [Visit Manhattan School of Music](https://www.msmnyc.edu/){:target="_blank"}

5. New England Conservatory - Located in Boston, Massachusetts, New England Conservatory offers a Bachelor of Music in Classical Guitar Performance. They have a distinguished faculty and provide numerous performance opportunities for students. [Visit New England Conservatory](https://necmusic.edu/){:target="_blank"}

6. Peabody Institute of the Johns Hopkins University - Situated in Baltimore, Maryland, Peabody Institute offers a Bachelor of Music in Guitar Performance. They have a comprehensive curriculum that includes private lessons, ensemble work, and music theory. [Visit Peabody Institute](https://peabody.jhu.edu/){:target="_blank"}

These colleges provide excellent training and opportunities for aspiring guitarists. Make sure to visit their websites for more detailed information about their programs, admission requirements, and faculty.
